name: A-Maize-ing Maze 2 Return of the Corny Title
name_original: A-Maize-ing Maze 2 Return of the Corny Title
description:
"A-Maize-ing Maze 2 Return of the Corny Title" is a game where you try to collect as many pumpkins as you can within the time limit.

Certain pumpkins give speed boosts or additional time so keep an eye out.

Click in the Game and allow the webpage to lock the mouse cursor!
